g\" alt=\"uvita costa rica things to do humpback whales\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"299\" alt=\"uvita costa rica things to do humpback whales\" class=\"wp-image-72554 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/30164754\/uvita-24.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/30164754\/uvita-24-800x532.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/30164754\/uvita-24-1080x718.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/30164754\/uvita-24-450x299.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/30164754\/uvita-24-30x20.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/30164754\/uvita-24-163x108.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/30164754\/uvita-24-271x180.jpg 271w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/30164754\/uvita-24-768x511.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/30164754\/uvita-24-1024x681.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/30164754\/uvita-24-1440x958.jpg 1440w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/30164754\/uvita-24-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/30164754\/uvita-24-600x399.jpg 600w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/30164754\/uvita-24-30x20.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/30164754\/uvita-24.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Many tour operators offer whale-watching tours in Uvita. There are signs all over town that read: &#x2018;Ballena&#x2019; (Spanish for whale). You can either book in advance online or at one of the offices in town. It&#x2019;s good to book your trip in advance during the whale season.&#xA0;<a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/uvita-whale-tour\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Book your whale watching tour online here<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n                <div data-vi-partner-id=\"P00037894\" data-vi-language=\"en\" data-vi-currency=\"USD\" data-vi-partner-type=\"AFFILIATE\" data-vi-url=\"86152P2,148781P12\" data-vi-campaign=\"uvita-widget\" class=\"lazyload block-viator\" data-script=\"https:\/\/www.viator.com\/orion\/partner\/widget.js\"><\/div>\n            <\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-4-nauyaca-waterfall\">4. <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/costa-rica\/nauyaca-waterfalls\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Nauyaca Waterfall<\/a><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>If there&#x2019;s one thing to do in Uvita, it&#x2019;s to visit the <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/costa-rica\/nauyaca-waterfalls\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Nauyaca Waterfall<\/a>! It&#x2019;s named multiple times as the most beautiful waterfall in Costa Rica. There are two enormously powerful waterfalls on different levels with natural swimming pools at the foot. It&#x2019;s one of those places that looks as if it has come straight out of a movie scene.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n\n<a class=\"block-googlemaps\" title=\"Get our Google Maps Legend\" data-maptype=\"Costa Rica \" href=\"\/shop\/google-maps\/costa-rica\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n            <div class=\"block-googlemaps__container\">\n                <div class=\"block-googlemaps__co