he mangrove are about 50 minutes driving from Uvita on a very straightforward paved road that&#x2019;s accessible for any car.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Good to know: <\/strong>We once learned in <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/malaysia\/langkawi\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Langkawi, Malaysia<\/a>, that mangroves protect our shorelines as wave breakers, to prevent erosion, and as a natural shelter for many animals in need. Malaysians are now planting back what they took to let mother nature do her work.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/26205446\/uvita-17.jpg\" alt=\"crocodile mangrove tour costa rica\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"300\" alt=\"crocodile mangrove tour costa rica\" class=\"wp-image-72369 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/26205446\/uvita-17.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/26205446\/uvita-17-800x534.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/26205446\/uvita-17-1080x721.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/26205446\/uvita-17-450x300.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/26205446\/uvita-17-30x20.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/26205446\/uvita-17-163x109.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/26205446\/uvita-17-270x180.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/26205446\/uvita-17-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/26205446\/uvita-17-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/26