rseback-riding tour. Walk the peaceful trails through the river and over the beach, and your guide explains more about the Costa Rican plants and animals. Before riding horses always look at the horse&#x2019;s body, the condition of their hooves, and the way the guide treats the horses. So far, we have found that Rancho La Merced is the best one in Uvita.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--tip \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--tip\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/tips\/wildlife-tourism\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Learn more about how animal are used in tourism and the better alternatives<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/30163459\/uvita-19.jpg\" alt=\"uvita costa rica things to do horseback riding\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"310\" alt=\"uvita costa rica things to do horseback riding\" class=\"wp-image-72544 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/30163459\/uvita-19.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/30163459\/uvita-19-800x551.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/30163459\/uvita-19-1080x744.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/30163459\/uvita-19-450x310.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/30163459\/uvita-19-30x21.jpg 3