selling fresh coconuts. Playa Hermosa is a short drive from Uvita, and the large parking is accessible for any kind of car. Have a serene beach to yourself by visiting in the mornings.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--tip block-link--long\">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--tip\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Tip<\/strong>: Take a <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/plastic-free-straws\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">stainless steel straw<\/a> with you to drink from the coconut and scrape out the coconut flesh. Here are <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/tips\/reduce-plastic-travel\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">our best tips for traveling plastic-free<\/a>!<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/31054243\/uvita-39-540x810.jpg\" alt=\"playa hermosa uvita beach\"><\/noscript><img width=\"225\" height=\"338\" alt=\"playa hermosa uvita beach\" class=\"wp-image-72593 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 540px) 100vw, 540px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/31054243\/uvita-39-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/31054243\/uvita-39-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/31054243\/uvita-39-225x338.jpg 225w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/upload