n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-10-sunset-at-uvita-beach-playa-uvita\">10. Sunset at Uvita Beach (Playa Uvita)<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>See the sun disappear on the horizon and the sky turning orange\/pink at Playa Uvita. Every day many people with their dogs hang out at Uvita Beach to experience the amazing sunsets it has to offer.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--mustread \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--mustread\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p>Also visit: <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/costa-rica\/santa-teresa\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">The coastal paradise Santa Teresa in Costa Rica<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/26202056\/uvita-13.jpg\" alt=\"playa hermosa uvita costa rica\"><\/noscript><img width=\"237\" height=\"338\" alt=\"playa hermosa uvita costa rica\" class=\"wp-image-72361 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1348px) 100vw, 1348px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/26202056\/uvita-13.jpg 1348w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/26202056\/uvita-13-421x600.jpg 421w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/26202056\/uvita-13-569x810.jpg 569w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/26202056\/uvita-13-237x338.jpg 237w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/26202056\/uvita-13-21x30.jpg 21