" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Italian<\/a> glass of wine watching the sunset.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--hotels \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--hotels\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p>Also see: <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/hotels-uvita\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">All hotels in Uvita<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/31054231\/uvita-38-540x810.jpg\" alt=\"sunset dinner Gusto Italian uvita\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"sunset dinner Gusto Italian uvita\" class=\"wp-image-72591 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 540px) 100vw, 540px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/31054231\/uvita-38-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/31054231\/uvita-38-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/31054231\/uvita-38-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/31054231\/uvita-38-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/31054231\/uvita-38-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/31054231\/uvita-38-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/31054231\/uvita-38-512x768.jpg 512w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-c