w.saltinourhair.com\/costa-rica\/manuel-antonio\/\">Manuel Antonio<\/a> by car. The highway towards Uvita is perfectly paved, and you will not need a 4&#xD7;4 vehicle to visit Uvita. Do check with your hotel if it&#x2019;s necessary since they could be located up a steep hill. We recommend using Waze instead of Google Maps because it leads you along easier roads (even though the other road seems shorter, it isn&#x2019;t).&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--transport block-link--long\">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--transport\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p>If you&#x2019;re planning to <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/costa-rica\/rent-car-costa-rica\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">rent a car in Costa Rica<\/a>, we recommend using <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/sunnycars-en-costa-rica\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Sunny Cars<\/a> because all insurances needed are included in the price <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/sunnycars-en-costa-rica\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">displayed on their website<\/a>. No hidden costs.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/30180321\/uvita-30.jpg\" alt=\"travel costa rica by car\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"travel costa rica by car\" class=\"wp-image-72575 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/30180321\/uvita-30.jpg 1536w, http